ZH: 我在意你的感受。
EN: I care about your feelings.
ZH: 她在意他的看法。
EN: She cares about his opinion.
ZH: 我们应该在意环境保护。
EN: We should care about environmental conservation.
ZH: 我在意他的健康状况。
EN: I am concerned about his health condition.
ZH: 他在意家人的幸福。
EN: He cares about the happiness of his family.
ZH: 请在意时间，别迟到了。
EN: Please pay attention to the time and don't be late.
ZH: 他对别人的评价不在意。
EN: He doesn't care about other people's opinions.
ZH: 在意自己的形象很重要。
EN: It is important to care about one's image.
ZH: 她不在意外界的闲言闲语。
EN: She doesn't mind idle gossip from the outside world.
ZH: 他在意你的回复。
EN: He is concerned about your response.
ZH: 不要在意过去的错误，继续前进。
EN: Don't dwell on past mistakes, keep moving forward.
ZH: 在意别人的意见是一种成长。
EN: Caring about other people's opinions is a form of personal growth.
ZH: 他一向不在意别人的看法。
EN: He has never cared about what others think.
ZH: 我在意你的安全。
EN: I am concerned about your safety.
ZH: 她在意自己的形象。
EN: She cares about her image.
ZH: 如果你在意，我可以帮你。
EN: If you care, I can help you.
ZH: 我完全不在意他的评价。
EN: I don't care at all about his opinion.
ZH: 我们必须在意健康问题。
EN: We must pay attention to health issues.
ZH: 尽管他们说了很多，但我不在意。
EN: Despite all they said, I don't care.
ZH: 谁在意那些无关紧要的事情呢？
EN: Who cares about those trivial matters?
